      • addPrefix

        private ResourceLocation addPrefix(java.lang.String name)
        Prefix the supplied name with the current mod id.

        If no mod id can be determined, minecraft will be assumed. The prefix is separated with a colon.

        If there's already a prefix, it'll be prefixed again if the new prefix doesn't match the old prefix, as used by vanilla calls to addObject.

        Parameters:
        name - name to prefix.
        Returns:
        prefixed name.
